{"tid":1653463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現今既警察100%係禽獸，唔該唔好再當佢地係人","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T10:22:07.000Z","uid":54303,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4430519deccdc188e3c50af155596e83cc54a140","tid":1653463,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"NOW新聞車長後腦中布袋彈被押  警署毆打兩小時後才被送院<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1653090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1653090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢班野獸管唔住自己既暴力衝動同性慾，令到無數無辜香港人受害，所以我請大家收起自己既同情心，對警察、警察家屬以及所有港共高官亳不留情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家要見到呢班人渣就要喊打喊殺，但係最低限度唔好勸交、唔好急救、商業杯葛做唔做到？最後，仲未同差佬親屬絕交既，快d send呢單新聞比佢再講聲「黑警死全家」啦。"},{"pid":"c401c97e2c0166abe43e690dbebc45265610bc02","tid":1653463,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fea51fada92d5b5b806e2088fc59787c102b9fa3","tid":1653463,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"而家係共產黨殖民政權vs香港平民<br />\n大家比少少骨氣"},{"pid":"4f1afa6795fb156b25f0b268e6388127e0ade152","tid":1653463,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78d7a941d99c7ed21d2770e6a844279f2c63a042","tid":1653463,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9ef8aa4e60a3b024a7a705ee07222d46fb5352e","tid":1653463,"uid":113056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"哥布林"},{"pid":"9e05e4b223feec1ef52502385df9902ad7e2c8ac","tid":1653463,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ef8aa4e60a3b024a7a705ee07222d46fb5352e","tid":1653463,"uid":113056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"哥布林"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"一樣都係綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo